### Passerelle Odoo — Requêtes de test
### Extension VS Code recommandée : "REST Client" (humao.rest-client)
### Remplacez la valeur de @cle par votre clé API personnelle.

@base = https://odoo-gateway-kappa.vercel.app
@cle = concours_vm0MF_Ujrf9y3k-OSbu_MhUihpr0Lk5c

### 1. Santé de la passerelle (public)
GET {{base}}/api/health

### 2. Mon profil candidat
GET {{base}}/api/me
Authorization: Bearer {{cle}}

### 3. Lister les projets
POST {{base}}/api/odoo/search_read
Authorization: Bearer {{cle}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "project.project",
  "fields": ["id", "name"],
  "limit": 20
}

### 4. Lister les employés
POST {{base}}/api/odoo/search_read
Authorization: Bearer {{cle}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "hr.employee",
  "fields": ["id", "name", "work_email", "department_id"],
  "limit": 50
}

### 5. Découvrir le schéma des feuilles de temps
POST {{base}}/api/odoo/fields
Authorization: Bearer {{cle}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "account.analytic.line"
}

### 6. Compter les tâches d'un projet
POST {{base}}/api/odoo/search_count
Authorization: Bearer {{cle}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "project.task",
  "domain": [["project_id", "=", 5]]
}

### 7. Me retrouver dans Odoo par mon nom (-> employee_id)
POST {{base}}/api/odoo/search_read
Authorization: Bearer {{cle}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "hr.employee",
  "domain": [["name", "ilike", "VOTRE_NOM"]],
  "fields": ["id", "name", "work_email", "department_id"]
}

### 8. Créer une feuille de temps (employee_id explicite)
POST {{base}}/api/odoo/create
Authorization: Bearer {{cle}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "account.analytic.line",
  "values": {
    "name": "Saisie de test",
    "employee_id": 485,
    "project_id": 5,
    "date": "2026-06-19",
    "unit_amount": 2.0
  }
}

### 9. Modifier une feuille de temps
POST {{base}}/api/odoo/write
Authorization: Bearer {{cle}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "account.analytic.line",
  "ids": [1234],
  "values": { "unit_amount": 3.0 }
}
